c/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Sherrie Gossett\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32946:\"<p>Wondering how to manage Google Reviews to boost your SEO and business reputation?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The majority of consumers use Google Reviews to make buying decisions. The good news is there are easy steps business owners can take to ensure these reviews make a positive impact.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, you&#8217;ll learn 3 simple steps to successfully manage Google Reviews.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-find-google-reviews-of-your-business\">How to Find Google Reviews of Your Business</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-create-a-google-business-profile\">Create a Google Business Profile</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-do-google-reviews-impact-seo\">How Do Google Reviews Impact SEO?</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-manage-google-reviews\">How to Manage Google Reviews</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-how-to-get-inappropriate-google-reviews-removed\">Get Inappropriate Google Reviews Removed</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-increase-sales-by-featuring-top-reviews-on-your-website\">Increase Sales</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-make-the-most-of-your-seo-optimize-your-site\">Make the Most of Your SEO: Optimize Your Site</a><ul></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-find-google-reviews-of-your-business\">How to Find Google Reviews of Your Business</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you already have Google Reviews of your business you&#8217;ll find them by searching for your business name or niche, either in Google or in Google Maps.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"609\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-1024x609.jpg\" alt=\"star ratings in google maps\" class=\"wp-image-173176\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-1024x609.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-300x179.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-768x457.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-1536x914.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-2048x1219.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-600x357.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-101x60.jpg 101w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-maps-151x90.jpg 151w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Star ratings for businesses are visible in Google Maps. These are taken from Google Reviews of your business. </em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Along with your star rating average and total number of reviews, you can also see a summary of reviews by clicking on your business in Google Maps or by viewing your Google Business Profile. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"665\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-1024x665.png\" alt=\"google reviews in maps\" class=\"wp-image-173177\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-1024x665.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-300x195.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-768x498.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-1536x997.png 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-2048x1329.png 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-600x389.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-92x60.png 92w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-reviews-summary-139x90.png 139w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>In Google Maps, click on a business (like Bistro St-Malo above), to view a summary of related Google Reviews.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-create-a-google-business-profile\">Create a Google Business Profile</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you haven&#8217;t already created a Google Business Profile, set one up now. It&#8217;s free. Follow our step-by-step <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-google-business-profile-to-imrpove-local-seo/\">instructions here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A Google Business Profile displays contact and location information for a local business.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can add photos, offers, and other details like ecommerce products, and links to book appointments or reservations.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A star rating average (based on Google Reviews) of your business will also display in your profile, along with review excerpts.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"636\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-1024x636.jpg\" alt=\"google business profile brasserie blanc\" class=\"wp-image-170751\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-1024x636.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-300x186.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-768x477.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-1536x954.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-2048x1272.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-600x373.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-97x60.jpg 97w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-google-maps-145x90.jpg 145w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-theme-notice-box\" role=\"alert\">\n<p>Google Business Profile was formerly called Google My Business (or GMB for short).</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-is-a-google-business-profile-important-for-local-seo\">Is a Google Business Profile Important for Local SEO?</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Google <a href=\"https://support.google.com/business/answer/7091\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">recommends</a> a Google Business Profile to improve your local business&#8217;s search engine ranking.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>These profiles are perceived as the single most important local SEO ranking factor, according to a <a href=\"https://whitespark.ca/local-search-ranking-factors/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">recent survey</a> of marketing professionals.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Because of their prominent display, Google Business Profiles can capture the attention and persuade potential customers to patronize your store.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Your Google Business Profile will show up in searches of Google Maps and in the Google Maps app. Notably, the Google Maps app was the<a href=\"https://www.statista.com/statistics/865413/most-popular-us-mapping-apps-ranked-by-audience\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\"><em> </em>most downloaded navigation app</a> last year. This popular Android app is used not only for navigation but for finding places to eat, shop, and play.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-app-mobile-phone-652x1024.jpg\" alt=\"google maps app mobile phone\" class=\"wp-image-172983\" width=\"409\" height=\"768\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-do-google-reviews-impact-seo\">How Do Google Reviews Impact SEO?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Google cites 3 <a href=\"https://support.google.com/business/answer/7091\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">review factors</a> that influence your business&#8217;s ranking in local search results.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Review score</strong> (star rating average)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Presence of &#8220;High-quality <strong>positive reviews</strong>&#8220;</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Total number</strong> of reviews.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-impacting-consumer-decisions\">Impacting Consumer Decisions</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Since Google star ratings display across local search results (including Google Maps), their prominence influences people&#8217;s buying decisions.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.brightlocal.com/research/local-consumer-review-survey-2022/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">85%</a> of searchers consider the <strong>star rating average</strong> of a business to be “important” of “very important.”</li>\n\n\n\n<li>When comparing businesses, 76% of searchers consider which one has the <strong>higher average.</strong></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.brightlocal.com/research/local-consumer-review-survey-2022/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">73%</a> of local shoppers are swayed by the presence of <strong><em>recent</em></strong> reviews of a business.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-1024x640.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-173183\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-1024x640.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-300x187.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-768x480.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-1536x960.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-2048x1279.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-600x375.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-96x60.jpg 96w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-maps-mister-walker-restaurant-144x90.jpg 144w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Star ratings appear in many areas of Google Search, including in Google Maps searches.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-manage-google-reviews\">How to Manage Google Reviews</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Using the SEO and consumer information above, you can adopt a review strategy that emphasizes:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Regularly asking for new reviews.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Increasing your star rating average.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-first-find-the-google-review-link-to-share\">First, Find the Google Review Link to Share</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Anyone who searches for the name of your business will see an option to &#8220;<strong>Write a review</strong>.&#8221; This option is displayed at the top right corner of your Google Business Profile.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"931\" height=\"684\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-write-review-button.png\" alt=\"google review write a review \" class=\"wp-image-172985\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-write-review-button.png 931w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-write-review-button-300x220.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-write-review-button-768x564.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-write-review-button-600x441.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-write-review-button-82x60.png 82w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-write-review-button-123x90.png 123w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But Google also provides local business owners with a <strong>shareable link</strong>. This is useful since you can add it to email messages, on your website, or in live chat messaging with customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here&#8217;s how to get that shareable link.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Log in to the Gmail account you used to create your Google Business Profile.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Then google your business&#8217;s name.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>At the top of search results you&#8217;ll see options for editing your profile.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Click on <strong>Ask for reviews</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"498\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1-1024x498.png\" alt=\"manage google reviews\" class=\"wp-image-173187\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1-1024x498.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1-300x146.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1-768x374.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1-600x292.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1-123x60.png 123w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1-185x90.png 185w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/ask-for-google-reviews-1.png 1169w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>That will open a new window. Click <strong>Get more reviews </strong>at the top right.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"377\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews-1024x377.png\" alt=\"google get more reviews\" class=\"wp-image-172996\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews-1024x377.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews-300x110.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews-768x283.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews-600x221.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews-163x60.png 163w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews-245x90.png 245w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/gbp-get-more-reviews.png 1296w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you&#8217;ll see your shareable <strong>Review link</strong>. Copy it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"982\" height=\"546\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-review-link.png\" alt=\"google reviews link\" class=\"wp-image-172999\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-review-link.png 982w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-review-link-300x167.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-review-link-768x427.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-review-link-600x334.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-review-link-108x60.png 108w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-review-link-162x90.png 162w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep that shareable link somewhere you can easily access it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you&#8217;re ready to plan the next steps.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-ask-for-reviews\">Ask for Reviews</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Regularly asking customers to review you on Google will increase the total number of reviews you have. And it can help sway those searchers who are influenced by<em> recency</em> of reviews.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To get more customer reviews we recommend that you add requests to your routine business sales and support communications.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some suggestions:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Verbal requests</strong>: Physical stores or businesses that provide local services can have staff work a verbal request into their final face-to-face communication with a customer.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Email requests</strong>: Businesses that routinely obtain the email addresses of their customers can schedule an automated email to go out after a purchase, requesting a review. (<em>Schedule an automated resend of any email that hasn&#8217;t been opened in a set time frame</em>.)</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>In-app notifications</strong>: Software app businesses can add an in-app notification that requests a review.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Physical store displays</strong>: Add window stickers or posters requesting reviews. Google offers a free downloadable <a href=\"https://marketingkit.withgoogle.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">marketing kit</a> with designs for you to use.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"524\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit-1024x524.jpg\" alt=\"google business profile marketing kit\" class=\"wp-image-173001\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit-1024x524.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit-300x154.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit-768x393.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit-600x307.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit-117x60.jpg 117w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit-176x90.jpg 176w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/google-business-profile-marketing-kit.jpg 1352w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend that any staff involved in requesting reviews,</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Click the link for themselves so they&#8217;ll be familiar with what customers will see.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Leave a review on a business they&#8217;ve patronized.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>This way, they&#8217;ll be better able to assist customers who have questions.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You may also want to provide instructions on your website, so you can refer customers there.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-theme-notice-box\" role=\"alert\">\n<p>Your customers won&#8217;t need a Gmail account to leave a Google Review. However, they will need a Google account. A Google account is a username and password used to log into Google products like Google Docs, YouTube, or Google Meet video conferencing.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-increase-your-review-score\">Increase Your Review Score</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend that you set a goal to increase your review score. (This is your star rating average of all reviews.)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To create focus and get traction,</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Have support or sales staff report (in written and verbal form) the current rating average in your weekly staff meetings.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Regularly track and report at least one other measure of customer satisfaction.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>If need be, improve your customer support process.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>This is a tactic we follow in our own business and it works.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-respond-promptly\">Respond Promptly</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>By responding promptly to reviews you communicate that you care about customer feedback. That can send a positive signal to searchers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do follow up on both positive and negative reviews.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Remember:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>People can edit their reviews. After receiving stellar support, that customer may turn a bad review into a good one.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>&#8220;Customers find a mix of positive and negative reviews <strong>more trustworthy</strong>,&#8221; <a href=\"https://support.google.com/business/answer/3474122?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Google reports</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a difficult customer that no amount of support will placate? Follow <a href=\"https://www.helpscout.com/blog/firing-a-customer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">these helpful tips</a> and move on.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-how-to-get-inappropriate-google-reviews-removed\">How to Get Inappropriate Google Reviews Removed</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>On occasion someone who&#8217;s not a customer of yours may leave a negative review of your business.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>They may have mistaken your business for another.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Or they might be a troll.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Follow <a href=\"https://support.google.com/business/answer/4596773\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">these instructions</a> to get Google to remove the review.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-increase-sales-by-featuring-top-reviews-on-your-website\">Increase Sales by Featuring Top Reviews on Your Website</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Rave reviews provide prospects with social proof they want before they buy. Embedding top reviews on a website is a proven way to boost sales.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend that WordPress site owners use the <a href=\"https://smashballoon.com/reviews-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">Smash Balloon plugin</a> to embed online reviews on their website.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>It takes only a few minutes to set up. (No technical knowledge required.)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Top reviews will automatically be selected to be shown.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>You can include reviews from other sites like Yelp or Facebook if you like.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Smash Balloon stands out because it&#8217;s optimized for speed, and page speed is an SEO ranking factor. You can also use it to embed social media feeds without bogging down your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Embed Reviews on your WordPress Website | Embed Reviews From Google, Facebook, Tripadvisor and Yelp\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/RElJPxCIzjo?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We&#8217;ve covered how Google Reviews impact your local SEO. To give yourself every advantage with Google&#8217;s algorithms, you&#8217;ll want to optimize your website too.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-make-the-most-of-your-seo-optimize-your-site\">Make the Most of Your SEO: Optimize Your Site</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Google makes it clear that your website ranking impacts how visible your business is in local searches and Google Maps.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, in addition to setting up a Google Business Profile, and managing reviews, it&#8217;s wise to optimize your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is where a plugin like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</a> comes in. It provides a beginner-friendly way to handle SEO tasks.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"485\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-140989\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-1024x485.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-768x364.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-600x284.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-127x60.png 127w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage-190x90.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/aioseo-homepage.png 1260w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO makes handling technical SEO tasks simple: you&#8217;ll click some buttons and fill out some forms.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, AIOSEO provides simple recommendations for improvement of your content.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Currently, All in One SEO (AIOSEO) is used on over 3 million sites. And it&#8217;s racked up thousands of 5-star ratings on WordPress.org.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Opt for the<a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\"> Plus or Pro version</a> of the plugin to get the Local SEO features.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-set-up-local-seo-basics\">Set Up Local SEO Basics</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\">downloaded</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\">installed the plugin</a>, you can set up your local SEO basics. This only takes a few minutes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the left-hand column of your WordPress admin go to <strong>AIOSEO » Local SEO</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"454\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-1024x454.jpg\" alt=\"aioseo local seo\" class=\"wp-image-154766\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-1024x454.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-300x133.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-768x340.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-1536x680.jpg 1536w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-2048x907.jpg 2048w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-600x266.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-135x60.jpg 135w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-menu-203x90.jpg 203w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now you’ll see 3 tabs: one for business location(s), one for opening hours, and one for map.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"478\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-1024x478.png\" alt=\"aioseo local seo settings\" class=\"wp-image-154770\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-1024x478.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-300x140.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-768x359.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-600x280.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-128x60.png 128w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings-193x90.png 193w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-local-seo-settings.png 1353w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Click on each tab and fill in the form.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This local SEO process adds code called <em>schema markup</em> to your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This helps Google understand your business and match it to relevant search queries.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-move-forward-with-on-page-seo\">Move Forward With On-Page SEO</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The next step is to begin learning how to optimize individual pages, like blog posts, so they rank higher in search engine results.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All in One SEO (AIOSEO) will make recommendations for each page of your site. Click on the recommendations to get instructions on what to improve.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We recommend bookmarking the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/blog/\">AIOSEO blog</a> and <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube channel</a>. Both have plenty of useful tutorials.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"466\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings-1024x466.png\" alt=\"aioseo general settings\" class=\"wp-image-173004\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings-1024x466.png 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings-300x136.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings-768x349.png 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings-600x273.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings-132x60.png 132w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings-198x90.png 198w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/aioseo-settings.png 1434w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some simple steps to begin your learning journey.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Learn what a title tag is and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-title-tags/\">how to optimize it</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn what a meta description is and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/\">how to optimize it</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn what alt tags are and how to <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/image-alt-text-vs-image-title-in-wordpress-whats-the-difference/\">add them to images</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn what a target keyword (<a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/using-the-focus-keyphrase-to-analyze-your-content/\">focus keyphrase</a>) is and how to use it.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn what <a href=\"https://www.blogtyrant.com/how-to-easily-find-the-best-keywords/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\">keyword research</a> is and how it can help your articles rank.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Learn what <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-rich-snippets-to-wordpress/\">rich snippets</a> are and how to add them to pages.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"493\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1-1024x493.jpg\" alt=\"rich snippet example\" class=\"wp-image-173009\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1-1024x493.jpg 1024w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1-300x144.jpg 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1-768x370.jpg 768w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1-600x289.jpg 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1-125x60.jpg 125w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1-187x90.jpg 187w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/product-schema-1.jpg 1070w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"><em>Learn how to </em><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-product-review-schema-in-wordpress/\"><em>add product schema</em></a><em> to get these types of search snippets.</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-bonus-seo-tips\">Bonus SEO Tips</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Business directory listings</strong> impact your ranking. And they&#8217;re easy to get. Move forward on this today with our guide <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-get-local-seo-citations/\">How to Get Local SEO Citations</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Reviews can provide valuable <strong>customer feedback</strong>. Learn from the positive and negative Google Reviews.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Google review policies</strong>: Google doesn&#8217;t allow misrepresentation or misinformation in reviews. Fake reviews and paid reviews are also policy violations. Find out more <a href=\"https://support.google.com/local-guides/answer/7400114?hl=en\">here</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Customer experience</strong>: Every business owner wants interactions and sales to result in happy customers. Take time to think through what you want the customer experience to be like: from when they first hear of your brand to when you ask for a review.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Plan for conversions</strong>: Make the most of your SEO efforts by planning calls-to-action (CTAs). WordPress users will like OptinMonster, a beginner-friendly, low-cost tool that&#8217;s effective in<a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/lead-generation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"\"> boosting conversions and sales</a>. (We use it too.)</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-summing-it-up\">Summing it Up</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Being proactive with Google Reviews is part of your online reputation management.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Good review management, plus business directory listings and website SEO, can elevate your visibility in google searches and influence consumer purchasing decisions.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-whats-next\">What’s Next?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you learn why Google Reviews are important and how to manage them for positive impact.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also check out our article <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-nap-in-seo/\">What is NAP in SEO?</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/small-business-seo-scams-how-to-detect-and-avoid-them/\" title=\"\">How to Avoid SEO Scams</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-manage-google-reviews-for-improved-seo/\">How to Manage Google Reviews for Improved SEO (Small Business Guide)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-manage-google-reviews-for-improved-seo/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"How to Write Meta Descriptions for SEO (Boost CTR &amp; Rankings)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:140:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 27 Mar 2023 14:27:36 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"how to write meta descriptions\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"how to write meta descriptions for seo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"meta description generator\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"meta descriptions wordpress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"https://aioseo.com/?p=37991\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:541:\"<p>Do you want to know how to write meta descriptions for SEO that’ll increase your organic search traffic, CTR (Click-Through-Rate), and rankings on Google? In this post, we’ll show you how to write meta descriptions for SEO, and to easily add them in WordPress. We’ll also cover what a meta description is and why you need it.</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/\">How to Write Meta Descriptions for SEO (Boost CTR & Rankings)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31791:\"<p>Do you want to know how to write meta descriptions for SEO that’ll increase your organic search traffic, CTR (Click-Through-Rate), and rankings on Google?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Research by <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Ahrefs</a> has shown that 74.98% of the top 10 ranking web pages have a meta description, which means it’s important to optimize yours for SEO.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you how to easily write meta descriptions for SEO and add them in WordPress. We’ll also cover what a meta description is and why you need it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s a quick overview of what we’ll cover in this post. Simply click on these quick links to jump straight to different sections:</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#what-is-a-meta-description-in-wordpress\">What Is a Meta Description in WordPress?</a></li><li><a href=\"#why-do-you-need-a-meta-description\">Why Do You Need a Meta Description?</a></li><li><a href=\"#how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo\">How to Write Meta Descriptions for SEO?</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-include-your-focus-keyword\">1. Include Your Focus Keyword</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-describe-your-pages-content\">2. Describe Your Page’s Content</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-include-a-call-to-action-to-increase-ctr\">3. Include a Call to Action to Increase CTR</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-be-unique-and-interesting\">4. Be Unique and Interesting</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#easily-add-your-meta-description-in-wordpress\">Easily Add Your Meta Descriptions in WordPress</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-use-the-ai-title-description-generator-to-effortlessly-create-meta-descriptions-with-1-click\">How to Automatically Add Meta Descriptions Using the AI Title/Description Generator (1-Click)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-adding-your-meta-description\">How to Manually Add Your Meta Description</a><ul></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-easily-double-check-that-youve-added-your-focus-keyword\">Easily Double-Check That You&#8217;ve Added Your Focus Keyword</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-analyzing-your-seo\">Analyzing Your SEO</a></li></ul></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Alright, let’s get started by first explaining what a meta description in WordPress is.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"what-is-a-meta-description-in-wordpress\">What Is a Meta Description in WordPress?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A meta description in WordPress is an HTML element or attribute that gives a brief summary of what your web page is about.&nbsp;It gives searchers a sneak peek of your article on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-serps/\" title=\"What Are SERPs (And Why Are they Important to SEO)?\">search engine results pages</a> (SERPs), hopefully encouraging them to click on your search listing.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s an example of a meta description on Google for the search query: “best keto recipes”:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"173\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/example-of-meta-description-on-google.png\" alt=\"Example of a meta description in Google\'s search results\" class=\"wp-image-33479\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/example-of-meta-description-on-google.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/example-of-meta-description-on-google-300x71.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/example-of-meta-description-on-google-600x142.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Google and other search engines often show the meta description in their search results. So by writing good, interesting and actionable meta descriptions, you can get more people to click through to your website and increase sales for your business.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"why-do-you-need-a-meta-description\">Why Do You Need a Meta Description?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Meta descriptions won’t directly help you rank, but compelling and actionable meta descriptions will convince more people to click on those links. More clicks mean more traffic, and it can also lead to higher rankings in search engines.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additionally, meta descriptions let Google know what your page is about. Even though Google doesn’t always use your meta description and sometimes adds its own based on your content, you should write them in case it does. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Writing good meta descriptions is especially important for your homepage, product and category pages since they help in establishing your brand.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo\">How to Write Meta Descriptions for SEO?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to writing meta descriptions for SEO, you should do the following:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol>\n<li>Include Your Focus Keyword&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Describe Your Page’s Content&nbsp;</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Include a Call to Action </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Make Them Unique and Interesting</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<p>We understand that this can feel like a lot&#8230;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8230;but depending on the niche you’re active in and the purpose of your site, you should at least try to implement as many of the above as possible to maximize your search traffic, clicks, and rankings. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s dig in a bit deeper&#8230;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-1-include-your-focus-keyword\">1. Include Your Focus Keyword</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Every meta description should include the focus keyword or keyphrase that you want to rank for.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Always start by <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-keyword-analysis-tool/\" title=\"8 Best SEO Keyword Analysis Tools You Need to Know in 2023\">performing keyword research</a> to find the best keywords for your content that have search volume and will match the search intent.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Adding your focus keyword is also important because Google highlights search terms by bolding them when they match the user’s search terms. This helps users to notice them more easily.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, here you can see how Google has highlighted the search terms from the search query: “best SEO plugin for WordPress”:</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"213\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-example.png\" alt=\"Example of how to write meta descriptions and including the keyword.\" class=\"wp-image-172152\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-example.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-example-300x91.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-example-600x182.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-example-190x58.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-example-297x90.png 297w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>As you can see, it only takes a second to scan this meta description to see that it answers the search query, resulting in more clicks and higher rankings.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-2-describe-your-pages-content\">2. Describe Your Page’s Content</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A good meta description should describe your page’s content. The recommended character limit is 155-160 characters, so you need to summarize your most important content in about 2 sentences.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO will help you get the right length. It shows how many characters you&#8217;ve used and warns if you exceed the max recommended characters for your meta description. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"173\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/max-recommended-characters-meta-description-in-asioseo.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-38156\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/max-recommended-characters-meta-description-in-asioseo.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/max-recommended-characters-meta-description-in-asioseo-300x71.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/max-recommended-characters-meta-description-in-asioseo-600x142.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/max-recommended-characters-meta-description-in-asioseo-190x45.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/max-recommended-characters-meta-description-in-asioseo-380x90.png 380w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>As easy as 1-2-3!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-3-include-a-call-to-action-to-increase-ctr\">3. Include a Call to Action to Increase CTR</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A call to action can prompt searchers not only to click on your link but also to do something once they arrive on your site. For example, <a href=\"https://wpforms.com/best-business-voip-and-internet-phone-systems/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">call a phone number</a>, sign up for a free trial, or take a special action.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here’s an example of MonsterInsights meta description, which lets people know that they can <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-set-up-google-analytics-on-a-wordpress-site/\" title=\"How to Set Up Google Analytics on a WordPress Site (Easy Way)\">set up Google Analytics for WordPress</a> with just a few clicks:&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"147\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/call-to-action-meta-description-1.png\" alt=\"Call to action meta description for the best analytics plugin for WordPress MonsterInsights\" class=\"wp-image-38158\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/call-to-action-meta-description-1.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/call-to-action-meta-description-1-300x60.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/call-to-action-meta-description-1-600x121.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/call-to-action-meta-description-1-190x38.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/call-to-action-meta-description-1-447x90.png 447w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, the stats of 12 million downloads will also work as proof that other website owners are using the plugin and encourage searchers to download it as well. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-4-be-unique-and-interesting\">4. Be Unique and Interesting</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Many large sites auto-populate their meta descriptions, so the first thing you should do is to make sure they’re unique and interesting.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ask yourself this question: Would the meta description spike your interest to want to know more and click on the link? Put yourself in your customer’s shoes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Does this sound overwhelming?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>No need to worry because AIOSEO helps you easily write meta descriptions for SEO and add them to your site in a heartbeat, which we’ll show you next.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"easily-add-your-meta-description-in-wordpress\">Easily Add Your Meta Descriptions in WordPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the easiest ways to add meta descriptions in WordPress is to use a powerful SEO plugin like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"447\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/all-in-one-seo-homepage.png\" alt=\"The best WordPress SEO plugin, All in One SEO\" class=\"wp-image-26967\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/all-in-one-seo-homepage.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/all-in-one-seo-homepage-300x184.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/all-in-one-seo-homepage-600x367.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">AIOSEO</a> is a powerful yet easy-to-use SEO plugin that has been downloaded over 100 million times. Millions of smart bloggers use AIOSEO to help them boost their search engine rankings and drive qualified traffic to their blogs. That’s because the plugin has many powerful features and modules designed to help you properly configure your SEO settings. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Examples of the SEO features you get with AIOSEO  include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Search Statistics:</strong> This powerful Google Search Console integration lets you track your keyword rankings and see important SEO metrics with 1-click, and more.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Next-gen Schema generator</strong>: This is a no-code <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/announcing-aioseo-4-2-5-next-gen-schema-generator-to-improve-your-seo-rankings/\" title=\"Announcing AIOSEO 4.2.5: Next-Gen Schema Generator to Improve Your SEO Rankings\">schema generator</a> that enables users to generate and output any type of schema markup on your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Redirection Manager</strong>: Helps you manage redirects and eliminate 404 errors, making it easier for search engines to crawl and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/index-your-website-on-google/\" title=\"9 Quick &amp; Easy Ways to Index Your Website on Google\">index your site</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Link Assistant</strong>: Powerful internal linking tool that <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-link-assistant-can-save-you-time-on-internal-and-external-link-building/\" title=\"6 Ways Link Assistant Can Save You Time On Internal Link Building\">automates building links</a> between pages on your site. It also gives you an audit of outbound links.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Rich Snippets Schema</strong> — add schema markup to your pages and get more clicks and traffic with <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-rich-snippets-to-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Add Rich Snippets to WordPress (The Easy Way)\">rich snippets</a>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Local Business SEO</strong> — boost rankings for all your Business Listings and get featured in <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/a-complete-local-seo-checklist/\" title=\"A Complete Local SEO Checklist: 10 Tips to Improve Rankings\">Google’s Knowledge Panel and Google Maps</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>These are just a few awesome SEO tools and features you can access with AIOSEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To get started adding and optimizing meta descriptions to your articles, you first need to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">install and activate AIOSEO</a> on your website. If you’ve never installed a plugin before, you can check out WPBeginner’s guide on <a href=\"https://www.wpbeginner.com/beginners-guide/step-by-step-guide-to-install-a-wordpress-plugin-for-beginners/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">how to install a WordPress plugin</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-use-the-ai-title-description-generator-to-effortlessly-create-meta-descriptions-with-1-click\">How to Automatically Add Meta Descriptions Using the AI Title/Description Generator (1-Click)</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the easiest ways to create meta descriptions is using AIOSEO&#8217;s <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/our-openai-integration-just-got-10x-more-affordable-now-using-chatgpt/\" title=\"Our OpenAI Integration Just Got 10x More Affordable – Now Using ChatGPT!\">AI Title/Description Generator</a>. This is a powerful tool powered by ChatGPT. The AI Title/Description Generator takes the labor out of crafting <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-title-tags/\" title=\"How to Write Great SEO Title Tags for Search Engines and People\">post titles</a> and meta descriptions, all with just the click of a button! </p>\n\n\n\n<p>All you have to do to use this game-changing <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-meta-description-generator-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Use a Meta Description Generator in WordPress\">meta description generator</a> is click on the robot icon next to the meta description field.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"194\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-1.png\" alt=\"Click the robot button to generate meta descriptions.\" class=\"wp-image-170245\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-1.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-1-300x83.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-1-600x166.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-1-190x53.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-1-326x90.png 326w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If this is your first time using this feature, you&#8217;ll be prompted to create an OpenAI account, and the setup wizard will walk you through the process of creating an account and connecting it to AIOSEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"496\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-openai-register.png\" alt=\"Create an account with OpenAI to get started using the AI Title/Description Generator.\" class=\"wp-image-170247\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-openai-register.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-openai-register-300x212.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-openai-register-600x424.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-openai-register-85x60.png 85w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-openai-register-127x90.png 127w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you&#8217;re done, you can continue auto-generating meta descriptions for your articles by clicking on the robot icon next to the meta description field. When you do this, the AI Title/Description Generator will generate 5 suggestions based on your content.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"462\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples.png\" alt=\"The meta description generator gives you 5 suggestions to choose from.\" class=\"wp-image-170248\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples-300x197.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples-600x395.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples-91x60.png 91w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/meta-description-generator-meta-description-examples-137x90.png 137w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Select the one you want by clicking the&nbsp;<strong>+</strong>&nbsp;button and tweak it according to your taste.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions on using this powerful meta description generator, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-use-a-meta-description-generator-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Use a Meta Description Generator in WordPress\">check out this guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-adding-your-meta-description\">How to Manually Add Your Meta Description</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To manually add meta descriptions to your articles, simply scroll down in the post or page you’re editing to the <strong>AIOSEO Settings</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"282\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-settings.png\" alt=\"Snippet preview in the AIOSEO settings\" class=\"wp-image-170337\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-settings.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-settings-300x121.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-settings-600x241.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-settings-149x60.png 149w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-settings-224x90.png 224w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Here you’ll first see a <strong>Snippet</strong> <strong>Preview</strong> that shows an example of how your content will look in search results based on the Title and Meta Description you enter.</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-using-smart-tags-in-your-meta-description\">Using Smart Tags in Your Meta Description</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>And to make it super easy for you to optimize your meta descriptions in WordPress, AIOSEO has added pre-installed smart tags with different variables you can use.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To start adding them, you need to scroll down to the <strong>Meta Description </strong>section and then click on any of the smart tags. In this example, we’ve added the <strong>+ Post Excerpt </strong>smart tag.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"211\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-post-excerpt.png\" alt=\"Adding your meta description using smart tags in All in One SEO\" class=\"wp-image-170344\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-post-excerpt.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-post-excerpt-300x90.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-post-excerpt-600x180.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-post-excerpt-190x57.png 190w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-post-excerpt-299x90.png 299w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO will then automatically add your post&#8217;s excerpt as meta description.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And you can also include other variables, such as <strong>+ Author First Name</strong> or<strong> </strong>+<strong> Author Last Name</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"385\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-smart-tags.png\" alt=\"View all smart tags in All in One SEO\" class=\"wp-image-170349\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-smart-tags.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-smart-tags-300x165.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-smart-tags-600x329.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-smart-tags-109x60.png 109w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-smart-tags-164x90.png 164w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To see all of the smart tags, click on the <strong>View all tags</strong> link.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"aioseo-manually-entering-your-meta-description\">Manually Entering Your Meta Description in WordPress</h4>\n\n\n\n<p>You also have the option to enter your meta description manually. Simply type in your description directly into the field.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"234\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-manual.png\" alt=\"Type in your meta description in the provided field.\" class=\"wp-image-170352\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-manual.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-manual-300x100.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-manual-600x200.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-manual-180x60.png 180w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo-manual-270x90.png 270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Don’t forget that the meta description should also include your focus keyword or keyphrase.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, with AIOSEO, you can also <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-add-emojis-to-your-seo-titles-and-meta-descriptions/\" title=\"How to Add Emojis to Your SEO Titles and Meta Descriptions\">add emojis to your meta descriptions</a>. Doing so makes them stand out on SERPs, resulting in a <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-to-increase-your-organic-clickthrough-rates/\" title=\"8 Proven Ways to Increase Your Organic Clickthrough Rates\">boost in clicks</a> and SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-easily-double-check-that-youve-added-your-focus-keyword\">Easily Double-Check That You&#8217;ve Added Your Focus Keyword</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>With AIOSEO, you even get an analysis of your focus keyword or keyphrase. It&#8217;ll check that you’ve used it in the meta description and other areas that&#8217;ll help to improve your SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"350\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/focus-keyphrase-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo.png\" alt=\"Analyzing the focus keyphrase in meta description in All in One SEO\" class=\"wp-image-37999\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/focus-keyphrase-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/focus-keyphrase-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-300x144.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/focus-keyphrase-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-600x288.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/focus-keyphrase-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-125x60.png 125w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/focus-keyphrase-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-188x90.png 188w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This helps ensure that your meta descriptions are SEO-friendly.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-analyzing-your-seo\">Analyzing Your SEO</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO makes it easy to improve your SEO with its SEO analysis tool.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the <strong>Basic SEO</strong> section, you can view an SEO analysis of your whole page&#8217;s content and get tons of helpful tips to boost your overall SEO score.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"369\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-basic-seo-1.png\" alt=\"Basic SEO analysis in All in One SEO\" class=\"wp-image-37351\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-basic-seo-1.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-basic-seo-1-300x152.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-basic-seo-1-600x303.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-basic-seo-1-119x60.png 119w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-basic-seo-1-178x90.png 178w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It tells you what you’ve optimized well and gives recommendations on what you need to improve (which will be marked in red).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The <strong>Page Analysis</strong> even analyzes your <strong>Title</strong> and gives immediate results on the title length, if the title has a number, and includes <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/700-power-words-that-will-boost-your-conversions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">power words or sentiment words</a>. These are important factors to attract more clicks.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"241\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/title-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-1.png\" alt=\"SEO title analysis in All in One SEO\" class=\"wp-image-33477\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/title-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-1.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/title-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-1-300x99.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/title-analysis-in-all-in-one-seo-1-600x198.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The<strong> Readability</strong> tool is also useful since Google has increased its focus on how well your content reads and is structured.&nbsp;The longer you get users to stay on your page, the more useful Google thinks your content is and will favor it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"730\" height=\"551\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-readability.png\" alt=\"Readability analysis in All in One SEO\" class=\"wp-image-37353\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-readability.png 730w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-readability-300x226.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-readability-600x453.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-readability-79x60.png 79w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/aioseo-page-analysis-readability-119x90.png 119w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 730px) 100vw, 730px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>As you can see, the Readability analysis gives you lots of valuable tips on how to improve your content and boost your rankings on Google.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, if you also want to learn how to optimize your SEO title, you can check out <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-change-the-seo-title-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Easily Change the SEO Title in WordPress (Step by Step)\">how to change your SEO title in WordPress</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And there you have it!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Use these tips to start crafting compelling and actionable meta descriptions and watch your search traffic, click-through rate, and rankings improve quickly.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you learn how to write meta descriptions for SEO and easily add them to your WordPress site using AIOSEO. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ultimate-wordpress-seo-guide/\" title=\"Ultimate WordPress SEO Guide: Optimize Your Site in 2023\">ultimate WordPress SEO guide</a> or our list of <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-best-practices/\" title=\"SEO Best Practices: 20 Ultimate SEO Tips to Boost Rankings\">SEO best practices</a> to help you rank higher on search engines.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop.</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/\">How to Write Meta Descriptions for SEO (Boost CTR & Rankings)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-meta-descriptions-for-seo/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"How to Use a Google Business Profile to Boost Local SEO\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_